What are your disciplines?

00:05:48.220 --> 00:05:49.300 align:middle line:90%
What are your habits?

00:05:49.300 --> 00:05:50.350 align:middle line:90%
How do you think?

00:05:50.350 --> 00:05:51.410 align:middle line:90%
What do you feel?

00:05:51.410 --> 00:05:53.940 align:middle line:84%
