whatever your job is.

00:06:07.860 --> 00:06:10.750 align:middle line:84%
You forget what
you've just learned.

00:06:10.750 --> 00:06:12.180 align:middle line:90%
You put the tool away.

00:06:12.180 --> 00:06:13.470 align:middle line:90%
And you forget about it.

00:06:13.470 --> 00:06:18.330 align:middle line:84%
So it depends on how
much you put into it.

00:06:18.330 --> 00:06:20.190 align:middle line:84%
But there's of
course also people

00:06:20.190 --> 00:06:24.265 align:middle line:84%
