00:06:27.820 --> 00:06:30.290 align:middle line:84%
I'm just-- I can't-- I
need to do something else.

00:06:30.290 --> 00:06:34.380 align:middle line:90%
So it's two ways.

00:06:34.380 --> 00:06:37.070 align:middle line:90%
It pushes you and it pulls you.

00:06:37.070 --> 00:06:39.680 align:middle line:84%
But also you have to, of
course, make some effort.

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:43.970 align:middle line:90%
It's not an automatic plug.

00:06:43.970 --> 00:06:44.470 align:middle line:90%
It is.

00:06:44.470 --> 00:06:46.960 align:middle line:84%
But you know, it needs
a little bit of work.

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:48.840 align:middle line:90%
>> LILOU: We hear you.

