inside, spending some more time

00:06:56.420 --> 00:06:57.870 align:middle line:90%
inside rather than outside.

00:06:57.870 --> 00:06:59.000 align:middle line:90%
Tell us more about that.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:01.000 align:middle line:90%
>> HIRA: Yeah, that's the key.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:03.740 align:middle line:90%
That's the key.

00:07:03.740 --> 00:07:05.700 align:middle line:90%
