00:07:05.700 --> 00:07:10.610 align:middle line:84%
We came to this world, a
3D dimensioned reality,

00:07:10.610 --> 00:07:14.330 align:middle line:84%
where we believe that we need
to fix things on the outside.

00:07:14.330 --> 00:07:16.260 align:middle line:84%
So there's something
wrong on the outside,

00:07:16.260 --> 00:07:17.872 align:middle line:84%
so we're like I
need to fix this.

00:07:17.872 --> 00:07:18.830 align:middle line:90%
I need to do something.

00:07:18.830 --> 00:07:20.913 align:middle line:84%
I need to think something,
do something, whatever.

00:07:20.913 --> 00:07:21.930 align:middle line:90%
I need to change it.

00:07:21.930 --> 00:07:26.230 align:middle line:84%
We never really learn
unless we're a child,

00:07:26.230 --> 00:07:27.330 align:middle line:90%
we can still understand.

00:07:27.330 --> 00:07:31.480 align:middle line:84%
But we never really learned that
somebody says stop everything.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:32.660 align:middle line:90%
Close your eyes.

00:07:32.660 --> 00:07:35.080 align:middle line:84%
Going inside of your
heart and fix it

00:07:35.080 --> 00:07:37.390 align:middle line:84%
from there, from
your inside world.

00:07:37.390 --> 00:07:38.640 align:middle line:90%
Fix it from your heart.

00:07:38.640 --> 00:07:40.780 align:middle line:90%
Fix it in that way, you know.

00:07:40.780 --> 00:07:43.660 align:middle line:84%
And the more that you
tune into that, the more

00:07:43.660 --> 00:07:47.370 align:middle line:84%
that you feel your heart
and what it's telling you--

00:07:47.370 --> 00:07:51.575 align:middle line:84%
because your heart speaks to
you all the time, all the time.

00:07:51.575 --> 00:07:52.075 align:middle line:90%
It dreams.

00:07:52.075 --> 00:07:54.710 align:middle line:90%
Your heart dreams all the time.

00:07:54.710 --> 00:07:56.620 align:middle line:84%
So the more that
you tune into that,

00:07:56.620 --> 00:08:00.050 align:middle line:84%
the images or the feelings
or the thoughts or the

00:08:00.050 --> 00:08:02.910 align:middle line:84%
