the more you tune into that,

00:08:02.910 --> 00:08:04.790 align:middle line:84%
the more you will
change reality.

00:08:04.790 --> 00:08:07.860 align:middle line:84%
But from the inside out
and not from the outside.

00:08:07.860 --> 00:08:10.770 align:middle line:10%
>> LILOU: So it's the
