very subtle world.

00:08:38.370 --> 00:08:42.720 align:middle line:84%
It's not as tangible
as this world.

00:08:42.720 --> 00:08:46.420 align:middle line:84%
So if you're expecting to
see something as bright

00:08:46.420 --> 00:08:51.850 align:middle line:84%
